sources.description: Female outlaw Jean Loring (Stephanie Bachelor) and her gang are killing wild game out of season. PD - No Copyright renewal

sources.title: Springtime In The Sierras (1947) ROY ROGERS
sources.description:
Stars: Roy Rogers, Trigger, Jane Frazee 
 Director: William Witney

 Jean Loring has her men illegally killing and selling game. Roy suspects her and gets himself invited to stay at her ranch. Investigating he finds the freezer where the slaughtered game are kept. But he is caught, tied up, and left to freeze.

sources.title: Springtime in the Sierras (1947) Roy Rogers | Western Classic Color Movie
sources.description:
Tough in a scrap... Tops with a song... more thrilling than ever! A gang, headed by evil Stephanie Bachelor, is slaughtering game out of season. Roy finds the freezer where the meat is kept, but baddie Roy Barcroft finds him there. A famous fight takes place in the freezer. Roy, of course, wins it.

Director: William Witney
Writer: Sloan Nibley 
Stars: Roy Rogers, Trigger, Jane Frazee
Genres: Classics, Western
